                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-5/6">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-800">How UndoBharat Works</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Our platform makes it simple to report issues. Just take a photo of the problem, share your location, and describe the issue in a few words. Our system automatically routes your complaint to the appropriate authorities and tracks progress until resolution. You'll receive updates at every step, ensuring transparency and accountability.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
